{"tid":2186662,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"渣車應先避免意外發生，後追究責任","createTime":"2020-09-03T06:17:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-04T05:42:20.000Z","uid":252605,"like":5,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"0ce22dbf6df3d9fe717d17aa8cd5ea0463b21fc4","tid":2186662,"uid":252605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:17:39.000Z","msg":"FB小駕群組有人post 條片係關於佢右邊部車打燈cut 單白入屯門，但樓主就見狀篤油加速，差d 炒埋一碟，事後自稱唔識防衛性駕駛<br />\n<br />\n我認為樓主毫無疑問係一條仆街。雖然硬cut 就100% 錯，但眼見危險唔識去避，仲要增加意外發生嘅機會。 一旦撞咗，冚世界多得你地唔少<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n正確做法係唔好篤油照畀佢cut,，避咗個意外先，事後再1823 告發佢 instead of post 上小駕取暖... 咁撚鍾意取暖，難道條撚樣空虛寂寞凍？<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fa153d40be857c154d62702f4c1cf3fbd14711a4","tid":2186662,"uid":79471,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T06:19:31.000Z","msg":"正確方法係話整親腰骨再收錢"},{"pid":"80cdaa64110c87d9bbd0121a563bc7f800573be5","tid":2186662,"uid":252605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-03T15:18:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1b6bfb715aa0e2c0c5d8daded0f000fcba64df8e","tid":2186662,"uid":252605,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T00:29:36.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"11402007e83aac233c973630e61304c2cc027502","tid":2186662,"uid":83913,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T00:36:23.000Z","msg":"片都無條"},{"pid":"e0f8054645ad5e3f86dad5f0df4ccc954037dbaf","tid":2186662,"uid":209241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-04T00:37:15.000Z","msg":"又冇片<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gi